unpublishedAction.name: netFetchTransform

actionConfiguration.body:
(data) => {
		return data.map(d => ({
				mid: d.mid,
				order: d.bb_issue_date,
				connected: d.bb_combined_completion,
				hw_order: d.Combined_HW_order,
				installed: d.ms4,
				provider: d.provider,
				name: d.name,
				applicaiton: d.application_date,
				hw_cause: d.hw_cause,
				bb_cause: d.bb_cause,
				obbu: d.obbu,
				obbr: d.obbr,
				user: d.user,
				updatedAt: d.iso_dtg,
				comment: d.comment,
				bb_kpi: d.v2bbkpi,
    }))
	}
